<<fig-cmro2, fig.cap="CMRO$_2$ map (\\textmu mol\\,O$_2$/100g/min) computed from pCASL CBF $\\times$ OEF $\\times$ CaO$_2$ using default OEF = 0.35. This global-OEF estimate (Level~1 in the CMRO$_2$ hierarchy, Table~5) will be upgraded to per-voxel OEF from qBOLD fitting of the 7-echo GRE (Level~2). Median CMRO$_2$ = 109\\,\\textmu mol/100g/min, consistent with healthy adult values.", fig.height=3>>=
